::Zardus/DevilDuer::

Zardus nods as he recieves Nemesis' transmission. "I will send BloodyStrike, 
Devil, and Perndabot. They will be there shortly." he says into his 
comm-link. The mentioned bots hear his orders and fly/run off into the forest.
